KVM: s390: vsie: Allow CRYCB FORMAT-2

When the guest and the host both use CRYCB FORMAT-2,
we copy the guest's FORMAT-1 APCB to a FORMAT-1
shadow APCB.

This patch also cleans up the shadow_crycb() function.

